h instance as follows.\r\n```python\r\nclass SomethingDataset(Base):\r\n    def __init__(self, mode):\r\n        if mode == \"debug\":\r\n            self.class = [\r\n               \"classA\", \"classB\"\r\n            ]\r\n        else:\r\n           self.class = [\r\n               \"classA\", \"classB\", \"classC\", \"classD\", ...\r\n            ]\r\n   ...\r\n```\r\n\r\nCurrently we must do as follows.\r\n```python\r\nclass SomethingDataset(Base):\r\n   ...\r\n\r\nclass DebugSomethingDataset(Base):\r\n   # Reproduction of SomethingDataset\r\n\r\n```","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/blue-oil/blueoil/issues/1105/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/blue-oil/blueoil/issues/1105/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}